steps.name: I am on the home page
I hover over Get Started button
I click publish button
I enter right credentials for free verified user
I click login button
I click create new post button
I should land on Design and schedule page
I click select account link
I should be able to select an account
I started to enter my message
I should see via Circleboom note added at the end of message
I should be able to see post preview screen with clickable Post it button
I should be able to see post preview screen with clickable Add to my queue button
I should be able to see post preview screen with clickable Schedule button
I should be able to see upload media
I should be able to see giphy
I should be able to see unsplash
I should be able to see design on canva
click to post my message
I should see CONTINUE WITH FREE PLAN button
I should see clickable UPGRADE button
I click CONTINUE WITH FREE PLAN button
I should see a popup shows my message sent

name: Login from HomePage to Publish
description:
Agile story:
  As a user,
  when I am on the circleboom homepage
  and I hover over get started button
  and click publish button
  and I enter right credentials
  then I should go to my account page
